From Windows OOBE Screen: 
Shift-F10 

Run Powershell: 
powershell 

Set Execution Policy command: 
set-ExecutionPolicy bypass 

Install Autopilot Script: 
Install-Script -Name 
Get-WindowsAutopilotInfo -Force 
Select "Y" at prompt 

Run Script to import Hardware ID into Intune: 
Get-WindowsAutopilotInfo -Online 

Log in with 365 Admin Credentials to authenticate 

Once complete, device should now appear in Autopilot List ready to assign.
